06:50.458 --> 06:53.541
-Money, please.
-No. You gotta go. You gotta go, son.

06:53.625 --> 06:54.833
-I'm good.
-Man.

06:55.416 --> 06:57.166
-GI, GI.
-They don't have no age limit

06:57.250 --> 06:58.666
-on a bar in Vietnam, then?
-GI, GI.

06:58.750 --> 07:01.458
No, no, you gotta... Come on,
get him the fuck out of here.

07:04.541 --> 07:07.166
Money, money. GI.

07:07.666 --> 07:09.583
-There you go, all right.
-Twenty bucks.

07:09.666 --> 07:10.500
Go.

07:10.583 --> 07:13.375
