Those signs are great, thank you.

08:12.041 --> 08:13.125
Fake news.

08:13.208 --> 08:15.583
Uh-huh. See? That's what they all go to.

08:15.666 --> 08:17.041
-Fake news.
-Always go to that one.

08:17.125 --> 08:19.166
-Yeah.
-I'm tired of not getting mine, man.

08:19.250 --> 08:21.083
I feel you. I feel you.

08:21.875 --> 08:25.958
Been fucked my whole goddamn life, bruh.
Goin' for me!

08:26.041 --> 08:27.416
Shit. For real.

08:27.875 --> 08:30.000
-Huh.
-I mean, back in the day,

08:30.291 --> 08:32.708
-being a brother meant something.
-Yeah, man.

08:32.791 --> 08:34.125
We fought against the man.

08:34.208 --> 08:35.875
-We loved one another.
-Amen.

08:35.958 --> 08:39.166
We became ace boon coon blood brothers
out there in that damn jungle.

08:39.250 --> 08:40.083
-Preach on it.
-Yeah.

08:40.166 --> 08:42.208
-Stormin' Norm demanded it.
-He did.

08:42.291 --> 08:43.500
-Sure did.
-All right, come on.

08:43.583 --> 08:45.333
-Yeah.
-Here we go. Boom!

08:45.416 --> 08:46.833
-[all] Boom!
-All right, yeah.

08:53.125 --> 08:55.041
-Otis.
-Vinh.

08:55.625 --> 08:59.041
-This is our guide, Vinh.
-Hey, I'm Eddie.

08:59.625 --> 09:02.250
-Vinh.
-I'm Melvin, man.

09:02.333 --> 09:03.666
-Nice to meet you.
-How you doing?

09:03.750 --> 09:05.083
-[Vinh] Good.
-Paul, man.

09:05.166 --> 09:06.166
-Good to meet you.
-Yeah.

09:06.250 --> 09:09.375
Gentlemen, welcome back to Vietnam.

09:09.958 --> 09:11.416
-Thank you.
-[Melvin] Thank you, man.

09:14.625 --> 09:17.708
