without me as your guide is a big mistake.

09:28.875 --> 09:31.375
-We know that jungle, man.
-Yes, we sure do.

09:31.458 --> 09:32.791
-Oh, yeah.
-[low chuckles]

09:33.625 --> 09:35.625
[Vinh] Do you have
the necessary documents?

09:35.708 --> 09:37.041
[Otis] Yes, there you go.

09:39.166 --> 09:43.250
From the Pentagon...
and from the Vietnamese government.

09:44.500 --> 09:46.583
