against Vietnamese family.

10:42.916 --> 10:44.916
-Paul.
-Hey, man.

10:45.500 --> 10:48.666
Those could've been the dudes
that zapped Norm, that's all I'm saying.

10:48.750 --> 10:54.500
Will you raise your goddamn glass?
The American War is over. Come on.

10:56.416 --> 10:57.291
Come on, man.

11:02.708 --> 11:03.875
[in Vietnamese]

11:06.916 --> 11:08.083
[Otis] Whoo!

11:09.250 --> 11:12.791
