-Oh, yeah. Oh.

11:14.583 --> 11:17.083
-Feelin' the love.
-Oh, man. Look at him.

11:17.166 --> 11:18.416
-I tell ya.
-I know.

11:18.500 --> 11:19.416
[all chuckling]

11:21.916 --> 11:23.833
