15:20.208 --> 15:22.458
[Otis] Come on! Go!

15:23.083 --> 15:24.333
Move, move, move!

15:26.083 --> 15:27.041
[speaking Vietnamese]

15:34.208 --> 15:35.458
[Norman] Go, go, go!

15:38.333 --> 15:39.250
Go!

15:42.333 --> 15:44.166
