[Paul] Yo, come on in here.

17:03.291 --> 17:05.291
All right. Let's see what we got here.

17:12.250 --> 17:14.375
-[Melvin] Out of sight!
-[Paul] Great googly-moogly.

17:14.458 --> 17:15.708
You know what this means?

17:16.500 --> 17:18.000
We gold standard.

