1:30:05.458 --> 1:30:06.291
You got me?

1:30:06.375 --> 1:30:07.833
-[Otis] We got you, Blood.
-[Melvin] Got you.

1:30:08.208 --> 1:30:09.166
All right.

1:30:12.916 --> 1:30:14.083
One...

1:30:15.541 --> 1:30:16.583
two...

1:30:18.041 --> 1:30:18.875
three!

1:30:19.083 --> 1:30:20.333
[David screams]

1:30:20.500 --> 1:30:22.208
-Come on, man.
-[whimpers]

1:30:22.291 --> 1:30:23.916
[screaming]

1:30:27.000 --> 1:30:29.875
-[Otis] God is great.
-[grunting]

1:30:30.458 --> 1:30:31.375
