♪ What's going on
Yeah, what's going on ♪

1:54:52.416 --> 1:54:54.416
♪ Tell me what's going on ♪

1:54:54.500 --> 1:54:59.791
♪ I'll tell you what's going on, whoo ♪

1:54:59.875 --> 1:55:01.791
♪ Right on, baby
Right on ♪

1:55:02.416 --> 1:55:04.291
[scatting]

1:55:06.625 --> 1:55:07.458
♪ Right on ♪

1:55:10.000 --> 1:55:13.166
Their mind's weak.
They got no intestinal fortitude.

1:55:15.375 --> 1:55:18.333
Ain't as strong as Paul. No, no, sir.

1:55:18.833 --> 1:55:21.541
Ain't got the guts Paul got.
It ain't their fault.

1:55:23.166 --> 1:55:26.625
They was born weak. Otis and his ho.

1:55:27.958 --> 1:55:32.208
Car thieves, guttersnipes,
chain snatchers.

1:55:34.083 --> 1:55:38.791
They ain't snatching... my gold bars.

1:55:40.208 --> 1:55:42.583
Not Paul. No, sir.

1:55:43.833 --> 1:55:45.666
I ain't getting fucked again.

1:55:45.750 --> 1:55:48.750
Trying to fuck me
with that salt in the Vaseline.

1:55:52.333 --> 1:55:55.000
Not Paul. Not this time.

1:55:57.041 --> 1:55:57.875
No.

1:55:59.291 --> 1:56:04.708
Them son of bitches. Son of bitches.
Son of...

1:56:06.541 --> 1:56:08.000
Turned my own son against me.

1:56:14.208 --> 1:56:15.375
My own blood.

1:56:16.500 --> 1:56:17.583
God damn.

1:56:20.333 --> 1:56:21.250
Well...

1:56:23.666 --> 1:56:25.583
we gonna see who's standing in the end.

1:56:26.916 --> 1:56:31.958
I don't care what the VA say.
VA don't know shit from Shinola.

1:56:32.041 --> 1:56:36.375
Worst fucking doctors in the world.
Malignancy? Shit.

1:56:39.375 --> 1:56:41.291
You made me malignant.

1:56:43.750 --> 1:56:45.625
This fucking place here...

1:56:50.166 --> 1:56:55.083
bathed me in that lymphoma
Agent Orange herbicidal stew.

1:56:55.166 --> 1:56:57.583
Those army bastards,
they scorched the earth with it.

1:56:57.666 --> 1:56:59.916
Sprayed that shit in the air
and the water,

1:57:00.000 --> 1:57:04.791
my bloodstream, my cells,
my DNA, and my motherfucking soul!

1:57:07.333 --> 1:57:08.708
But I ain't dying...

1:57:09.791 --> 1:57:10.916
from that shit.

1:57:13.000 --> 1:57:14.208
You will not...

1:57:15.458 --> 1:57:16.750
kill Paul.

1:57:17.833 --> 1:57:18.916
You hear me?

1:57:24.250 --> 1:57:25.291
Hear me.

1:57:28.833 --> 1:57:32.083
You will not kill Paul.

1:57:34.333 --> 1:57:36.958
And the US government
will not take me out.

1:57:39.958 --> 1:57:41.416
I will choose

1:57:42.458 --> 1:57:43.375
when...

1:57:45.291 --> 1:57:47.541
and how I die.

1:57:48.958 --> 1:57:50.083
You dig?

1:57:51.166 --> 1:57:54.625
You couldn't kill me then,
with three tours,

1:57:55.291 --> 1:57:58.875
you sure in the fuck can't kill me now.

1:58:00.833 --> 1:58:01.833
Right on?

1:58:05.708 --> 1:58:06.833
Right on.

1:58:12.916 --> 1:58:14.166
Right on.

1:58:19.000 --> 1:58:20.916
Right on.

1:58:34.208 --> 1:58:36.625
[Otis breathing heavily]

1:58:42.541 --> 1:58:45.500
-I know that thing is throbbing like hell.
-Yeah.

1:58:46.750 --> 1:58:47.875
[pills rattling]

1:58:51.750 --> 1:58:52.666
Thanks.

1:58:53.416 --> 1:58:56.250
Don't thank me. Thank your Uncle Meli-Mel.

1:58:57.833 --> 1:58:58.958
You OGs.

1:59:06.833 --> 1:59:09.916
Hedy, he's running a fever.
I think that wound is infected.

1:59:23.833 --> 1:59:24.958
Look after him.

1:59:44.625 --> 1:59:46.166
[screaming and grunting]

1:59:47.625 --> 1:59:49.458
Get off me! Get off!

1:59:49.541 --> 1:59:51.541
[grunting]

1:59:53.291 --> 1:59:54.625
Get off!

2:00:00.083 --> 2:00:01.333
[in Vietnamese]

2:00:03.666 --> 2:00:04.875
[grunts]

2:00:14.625 --> 2:00:17.041
[Hedy] What's the issue
between you and your father?

2:00:21.625 --> 2:00:22.583
Jacklyn.

2:00:24.375 --> 2:00:25.583
Who is she?

2:00:30.875 --> 2:00:31.958
My mother.

2:00:35.333 --> 2:00:36.458
My mom...

2:00:39.750 --> 2:00:43.125
She had a very difficult delivery.

2:00:52.333 --> 2:00:53.875
And she didn't survive?

2:01:10.041 --> 2:01:11.500
My apology.

2:01:14.333 --> 2:01:18.166
I'm intruding. It's none of my business.

2:01:19.666 --> 2:01:20.916
My father...

2:01:23.958 --> 2:01:25.625
he loved her more than me.

2:01:28.083 --> 2:01:29.791
Never let me forget that either.

2:01:34.791 --> 2:01:37.500
He has hated me since the day I was born.

2:01:38.875 --> 2:01:40.333
[voice breaks] All my fault.

2:01:46.750 --> 2:01:49.750
[sniffles]
I should've died instead of my mother.

2:02:05.875 --> 2:02:09.041
[grunts] Goddamn snakebite. Come on.

2:02:10.875 --> 2:02:13.375
[yells] Mother... Fuck you!

2:02:13.916 --> 2:02:15.416
[screaming]

2:02:15.916 --> 2:02:16.791
Fuck!

2:02:19.083 --> 2:02:20.208
[groans]

2:02:21.958 --> 2:02:23.125
[grunts]

2:02:29.666 --> 2:02:30.708
[laughs]

2:02:31.208 --> 2:02:32.250
Oof.

2:02:33.125 --> 2:02:37.833
God, you're a trickster.
Oh, God. You're a trickster.

2:02:39.250 --> 2:02:42.416
[laughing] Come to Papa.

2:02:50.208 --> 2:02:51.291
[grunting softly]

2:03:08.083 --> 2:03:09.208
[groans]

2:03:22.708 --> 2:03:23.875
[exhales heavily]

2:03:36.291 --> 2:03:38.458
Oh, f-- [chuckles]

2:03:43.750 --> 2:03:46.666
You got it, Norm. All for you, baby.

2:03:48.125 --> 2:03:49.416
[laughing]

2:03:53.750 --> 2:03:55.000
Life is a bitch!

2:04:00.083 --> 2:04:03.250
If I gotta go out, I gotta go out
like a man, Blood.

2:04:04.666 --> 2:04:07.125
-Morals and ethics.
-Hmm.

2:04:07.208 --> 2:04:09.125
Sounds like Stormin' Norman.

2:04:11.958 --> 2:04:13.833
You know,
I keep hearing his voice in my head,

2:04:13.916 --> 2:04:16.041
telling me to do right,
just to get it right.

2:04:17.041 --> 2:04:17.916
[sighs]

2:04:19.375 --> 2:04:22.125
Stormin' had this whole living thing
figured out.

2:04:23.666 --> 2:04:26.208
We are not gonna die in Nam.

2:04:30.750 --> 2:04:32.291
Come on, let's battle, Blood.

2:04:47.708 --> 2:04:48.541
[both] Bloods.

2:04:48.625 --> 2:04:52.000
I was asleep. Man, I was fast asleep,
knocked out, man.

2:04:52.750 --> 2:04:54.250
God poked and woke me.

2:04:55.791 --> 2:04:59.125
I said, "God... God, why you
waking my black ass up?"

2:04:59.583 --> 2:05:04.250
God said to me,
"Paul, fuck them motherfuckers.

2:05:04.666 --> 2:05:06.166
Keep on keeping on."

2:05:08.000 --> 2:05:11.333
I said to God, "God, do what now?"

2:05:12.375 --> 2:05:14.416
God raised His voice, didn't yell,

2:05:14.500 --> 2:05:18.208
but put some bass
in that heavenly voice, said to me,

2:05:19.875 --> 2:05:23.000
"Fuck them motherfuckers, Paul.
They don't know shit.

2:05:23.500 --> 2:05:26.041
Do your thing. Show you're right."

2:05:47.166 --> 2:05:48.583
What you doing here, bruh?

2:05:50.541 --> 2:05:52.208
I've been wanting to talk to you.

2:05:53.666 --> 2:05:54.791
About what?

2:05:56.083 --> 2:05:57.125
You know.

2:06:00.875 --> 2:06:01.833
Go away, man.

2:06:03.416 --> 2:06:04.291
Please?

2:06:06.000 --> 2:06:09.208
No, no, come on now.
Come on now. Come on now.

2:06:10.583 --> 2:06:12.208
That I can't do, Paul.

2:06:17.916 --> 2:06:19.458
Gonna have to come clean.

2:06:20.958 --> 2:06:23.833
[gunshots echoing]

2:06:32.958 --> 2:06:35.166
[gunshots continue in distance]

2:07:09.750 --> 2:07:11.750
-[Paul exclaims]
-[soldier screams]

2:07:11.833 --> 2:07:13.291
[Paul] Hey, Norm! Norm!

2:07:19.000 --> 2:07:19.833
Hey.

2:07:23.500 --> 2:07:25.416
[groans softly]

2:07:51.250 --> 2:07:52.250
There it is.

2:08:08.375 --> 2:08:09.291
[Paul grunts]

2:08:15.333 --> 2:08:17.083
It was an accident.

2:08:20.958 --> 2:08:22.500
Ain't no thing, Blood.

2:08:24.833 --> 2:08:25.916
Accident.

2:08:29.666 --> 2:08:31.000
I forgive you.

2:08:33.041 --> 2:08:34.125
You hear that?

2:08:36.666 --> 2:08:37.750
I forgive you.

2:08:39.833 --> 2:08:41.000
Ain't no thing, Blood.

2:08:44.041 --> 2:08:45.166
Come on now.

2:08:46.750 --> 2:08:49.083
Come on, Paul. Come on, Blood.

2:08:52.750 --> 2:08:54.041
I forgive you.

2:08:57.791 --> 2:08:59.083
God is love.

2:09:00.833 --> 2:09:02.125
Love is God.

2:09:07.833 --> 2:09:10.375
Come on. Hey, you got me now.

2:09:12.250 --> 2:09:13.458
[Paul crying]

2:09:13.541 --> 2:09:16.791
You got me good. Ain't no thing.

2:09:18.041 --> 2:09:19.500
[Paul sobbing loudly]

2:09:26.208 --> 2:09:28.208
I'm sorr... [sobbing]

2:09:32.000 --> 2:09:34.833
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

2:09:36.875 --> 2:09:38.208
I know you, Blood.

2:09:40.500 --> 2:09:41.958
I died for you, Blood.

2:09:46.041 --> 2:09:49.208
[Quân] Keep digging. You're outnumbered.

2:09:51.166 --> 2:09:53.250
We're always outnumbered.

2:09:54.250 --> 2:09:55.333
Where's gold?

2:09:55.416 --> 2:09:57.291
Stormin' Norman took it, man.

2:09:59.458 --> 2:10:00.541
It was his.

2:10:00.958 --> 2:10:02.250
Who's Stormin' Norman?

2:10:03.416 --> 2:10:05.750
One bad black motherfucker.

2:10:06.916 --> 2:10:08.791
-Where's all the GI?
-[Paul grunts]

2:10:09.583 --> 2:10:12.000
No, I will never tell.

2:10:12.583 --> 2:10:17.416
See, we're Bloods. We got a bond.

2:10:18.791 --> 2:10:23.375
We fought... in a immoral war
that wasn't ours,

2:10:23.458 --> 2:10:27.291
for rights... for rights we didn't have.

2:10:29.250 --> 2:10:30.333
They're my brothers.

2:10:30.416 --> 2:10:32.291
You killed my brother.

2:10:35.041 --> 2:10:35.958
I did.

2:10:38.916 --> 2:10:43.250
♪ Don't go and talk about my father ♪

2:10:43.750 --> 2:10:48.208
♪ God is my friend
Jesus is my friend ♪

2:10:49.583 --> 2:10:53.666
♪ He made this world for us to live in ♪

2:10:55.166 --> 2:10:58.416
♪ And gave us everything ♪

2:10:59.000 --> 2:11:01.583
♪ All He asks of us ♪

2:11:03.666 --> 2:11:08.125
♪ Is we give each other love ♪

2:11:10.458 --> 2:11:12.958
-My brother, Marvin.
-You're drunk.

2:11:13.041 --> 2:11:15.791
-I ain't never been more sober in my life.
-Dig!

2:11:17.958 --> 2:11:20.166
Okay, it's deep enough, man.

2:11:20.791 --> 2:11:21.666
Okay...

2:11:22.750 --> 2:11:23.708
dig.

2:11:23.791 --> 2:11:25.583
[grunting]

2:11:26.333 --> 2:11:29.041
♪ Don't go and talk about my father... ♪

2:11:29.125 --> 2:11:30.125
Faster!

2:11:30.958 --> 2:11:32.125
♪ God... ♪

2:11:32.208 --> 2:11:33.041
[Quân] Faster!

2:11:33.125 --> 2:11:35.416
♪ ...Is my friend
Jesus is my friend ♪

2:11:35.500 --> 2:11:36.541
[Quân] Faster!

2:11:36.625 --> 2:11:37.666
♪ He loves us ♪

2:11:38.291 --> 2:11:39.125
Faster.

2:11:39.208 --> 2:11:41.958
♪ Whether or not we know it ♪

2:11:44.000 --> 2:11:49.625
♪ And He'll forgive us all our sins ♪

2:12:05.791 --> 2:12:07.041
[Melvin] You all right up there?

2:12:07.125 --> 2:12:08.583
-Keep your eyes open.
-On it.

2:12:08.666 --> 2:12:09.958
[Melvin] Kool and the Gang.

2:12:13.416 --> 2:12:16.958
After you've been in a war,
you understand it really never ends.

2:12:19.750 --> 2:12:24.125
Whether it's in your mind or in reality.
There are just degrees.

2:12:24.208 --> 2:12:25.750
Tell me about it.

2:12:30.166 --> 2:12:34.375
If I happen to die, send my share here.

2:12:42.125 --> 2:12:44.208
One of you two should have this.

2:12:44.291 --> 2:12:45.500
No. I don't want it.

2:12:45.583 --> 2:12:47.208
I ain't fired a gun in my life.

2:12:47.291 --> 2:12:50.083
I shoot, I'd probably miss by a mile,
especially with my leg.

2:12:54.166 --> 2:12:56.500
My father? You seen him?

2:12:57.166 --> 2:12:58.833
[Melvin] My hunch is Desroche is with him.

2:12:58.916 --> 2:13:00.958
-[Hedy] Who?
-One of your countrymen.

2:13:01.583 --> 2:13:04.333
He set up our deal,
probably gave us the old flimflam.

2:13:04.416 --> 2:13:06.166
Perhaps I could appeal to him.

2:13:06.666 --> 2:13:07.916
[Melvin] Worth a try.

2:13:09.041 --> 2:13:10.291
Are you ready for this?

2:13:10.875 --> 2:13:13.083
Blood, this ain't my first time in Nam.

2:13:31.583 --> 2:13:33.958
Well, if we live, you'll teach me that.
[chuckles]

2:13:34.041 --> 2:13:35.250
[Melvin] We're all gonna live.

2:13:35.833 --> 2:13:41.625
And maybe someday if I come to Paris,
you can show me the "Champs-Eleesees."

2:13:42.375 --> 2:13:43.583
[Hedy] The what?

2:13:43.666 --> 2:13:46.250
You know, the "Champs-Eleesees"?
That big thing y'all got.

2:13:46.333 --> 2:13:49.083
[laughs] The Champs-Élysées.

2:13:50.291 --> 2:13:51.750
-[Melvin] Bet?
-Bet.

2:13:54.083 --> 2:13:56.291
-Remember the plan.
-[Hedy continues laughing]

2:13:56.375 --> 2:13:57.500
Yes, sir.

2:14:03.291 --> 2:14:04.750
[vehicles approaching]

2:14:16.333 --> 2:14:18.125
[men chattering indistinctly]

2:14:38.125 --> 2:14:40.000
Who is your pretty companion?

2:14:41.250 --> 2:14:43.458
[in French]

2:14:43.541 --> 2:14:44.416
[Desroche] Ah.

2:15:03.625 --> 2:15:04.875
[in English] What'd he just say?

2:15:05.791 --> 2:15:08.375
That the green
is more important than black.

2:15:08.458 --> 2:15:10.125
[in French]

2:15:10.208 --> 2:15:11.875
[in English] He asks for Norman's share.

2:15:13.083 --> 2:15:15.416
[sighs] I don't know.

2:15:17.541 --> 2:15:20.291
Norman is pretty particular
about what he shares.

2:15:23.166 --> 2:15:25.291
-May I ask you a question?
-Yes.

2:15:27.666 --> 2:15:30.041
Was Tiên in on all this?

2:15:31.125 --> 2:15:34.833
Tiên is a very smart woman,
but she doesn't have the appetite

2:15:34.916 --> 2:15:38.375
for a venture like this.
She knows nothing about this.

2:15:39.333 --> 2:15:42.000
She is as innocent as you are ignorant.

2:15:45.625 --> 2:15:47.125
Well, take the gold and...

2:15:50.083 --> 2:15:51.333
leave in peace.

2:15:52.500 --> 2:15:53.375
Go with God.

2:15:54.333 --> 2:15:56.500
We just want what we came for.

2:15:56.583 --> 2:15:57.416
Good.

2:16:26.750 --> 2:16:27.958
[Quân] You bastards!

2:16:32.500 --> 2:16:34.125
[men yelling in Vietnamese]

2:16:44.791 --> 2:16:46.291
[groans]

2:16:52.666 --> 2:16:54.083
[Desroche] Go, go, go!

2:16:59.166 --> 2:17:00.625
[grunting]

2:17:02.083 --> 2:17:03.291
[swears in French]

2:17:05.666 --> 2:17:06.500
[groans]

2:17:19.833 --> 2:17:21.291
[Desroche grunting]

2:17:24.291 --> 2:17:26.458
[groaning]

2:17:28.958 --> 2:17:30.875
[groans loudly]

2:17:36.541 --> 2:17:38.750
-[Vinh] I can't feel a thing.
-Fuck.

2:17:39.833 --> 2:17:42.250
Straight through. Through and through.

2:17:42.333 --> 2:17:44.416
-You'll survive, buddy.
-[Vinh] Be safe.

2:17:44.500 --> 2:17:45.708
[gun firing]

2:17:59.833 --> 2:18:01.416
[groans]

2:18:12.375 --> 2:18:13.291
Grenade!

2:18:16.416 --> 2:18:18.416
No! [groaning]

2:18:23.791 --> 2:18:25.541
[continues groaning]

2:18:29.041 --> 2:18:30.916
[Desroche] Your Bloods are all dead.

2:18:32.416 --> 2:18:34.000
There is no one left.

2:18:40.125 --> 2:18:41.458
[in French]

2:18:42.708 --> 2:18:43.958
[in English] Where is the gold?

2:18:46.625 --> 2:18:51.625
Five Bloods don't die, we multiply.

2:18:54.750 --> 2:18:55.916
Allow me.

2:18:57.291 --> 2:18:58.416
[Desroche groans and thuds]

2:19:06.583 --> 2:19:07.708
[Otis laughing]

2:19:09.750 --> 2:19:13.500
Madness! Madness!

2:19:13.583 --> 2:19:15.083
[continues laughing]

2:19:24.708 --> 2:19:26.791
[David] Godfather, you'll be all right.

2:19:29.291 --> 2:19:30.416
[Otis laughing]

2:19:38.000 --> 2:19:40.000
[solemn instrumental music plays]

2:19:43.666 --> 2:19:44.875
[Paul]  Dear David.

2:19:46.625 --> 2:19:47.791
Son...

2:19:50.416 --> 2:19:53.750
if you're reading this,
you know I've met my maker.

2:20:04.916 --> 2:20:08.125
I gave this letter to... my main man,

2:20:10.041 --> 2:20:13.250
your godfather, Otis,

2:20:13.875 --> 2:20:15.541
when we landed back in Nam.

2:20:17.875 --> 2:20:23.833
I came back to confront the demons
that haunted me and tortured you.

2:20:25.875 --> 2:20:27.958
I made you feel like you weren't loved.

2:20:32.041 --> 2:20:38.000
Our brother Stormin' Norman always
commanded us Bloods, love one another.

2:20:40.500 --> 2:20:42.166
In that way, I failed you, man.

2:20:44.291 --> 2:20:46.000
All I can say to you is...

2:20:49.458 --> 2:20:52.041
I'm sorry I put you through holy hell.

2:20:56.916 --> 2:20:58.166
Believe me...

2:20:58.791 --> 2:20:59.958
This just came.

2:21:02.000 --> 2:21:03.375
[Paul]  ...it wasn't your fault.

2:21:06.208 --> 2:21:10.666
There are things about me that you
will never know or understand, David.

2:21:20.000 --> 2:21:21.916
I wish I could turn back
the hands of time...

2:21:33.583 --> 2:21:34.458
I can't.

2:21:40.583 --> 2:21:41.500
Nobody can.

2:21:46.625 --> 2:21:48.625
-[man] Mic check!
-[all] Mic check!

2:21:48.708 --> 2:21:50.333
-[man] Mic check!
-[all] Mic check!

2:21:50.416 --> 2:21:52.208
I got something I gotta share with y'all.

2:21:52.291 --> 2:21:54.916
We just received a check
from our soldier Eddie

2:21:55.000 --> 2:21:56.875
for two million dollars!

2:21:56.958 --> 2:21:58.625
[all cheering]

2:22:00.083 --> 2:22:02.083
-Mic check!
-[all] Mic check!

2:22:02.166 --> 2:22:04.500
-Mic check!
-[all] Mic check!

